{"tid":1890200,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗：想大力擁抱中國人 為他們加油！","createTime":"2020-02-21T05:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T15:04:30.000Z","uid":5134,"like":31,"dislike":147,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"da23978d938e7f201c7f088be800a66481dc1646","tid":1890200,"uid":5134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yFemqgT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyFemqgT.png&h=aa268165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n效力祖雲達斯的葡萄牙球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗），最近為其贊助商Nike進行一段直播訪問提到了中國爆發的武漢肺炎疫情，坦言要為中國人民祈禱，同時也稱效力愛斯賓奴的武磊是他的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n這段「一剔牌」的直播是一位小朋友來到祖記更衣室與C朗作短訪，為的是宣傳新鞋，但C朗在片段中說起他對武漢肺炎的關注：「中國人現在所承受的苦難，我此刻想藉這機會給他們一個大力的擁抱。我為他們加油，為他們祈禱，我期待今年或明年會再回到中國，這是一個美麗的國家。」<br />\n<br />\nC朗之所以提到中國，是因為來訪問的小記者提起同為一剔牌代言的武磊，而C朗則謂：「武磊是一位來自中國的球員，他是我的朋友。」"},{"pid":"a0160a492844ecda7df1c89fbf647be31838bc55","tid":1890200,"uid":218659,"like":102,"dislike":0,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:05:39.000Z","msg":"C朗(武漢肺炎）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9639b79531c378b887c3dc3665f620e7f0e366","tid":1890200,"uid":5649,"like":27,"dislike":6,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:06:36.000Z","msg":"希望條陷家產中肺炎啦"},{"pid":"c0708cd2a1ee1f50c24f86640acd9c8e2cc84f63","tid":1890200,"uid":32899,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美欺又贏"},{"pid":"1ddb32a7827c49ff860bf2a7fa6f200ef4c79ee8","tid":1890200,"uid":134997,"like":7,"dislike":52,"score":-45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"其實C朗只係做marketing 姐<br />\n唔好怪佢得唔得"},{"pid":"7f2c2b7869b8faabf15be65c64ed9ceef9dc4b4e","tid":1890200,"uid":55502,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"想<br />\n<br />\n真係抱？不了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p